Field Detail

HASH_STH_SIZE

public static final int HASH_STH_SIZE
The default size to be used for Hashtable, HashMap and HashSet. The default is 11 and it leads to big memory usage. Having a default load factor of 0.75, table of size 4 can take 3 elements before being re-hashed - a values that seems to be optimal for most of the cases.
